  "html": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">The focus of this repetition is on these sentences:</span></p><div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Sentence 1 - うん、いれて。= Yes, add some.</p><p>Sentence 2 - あ、いれないで。= Ah, don&#39;t add any.</p><p><strong>How to use this lesson</strong> - When the repeat message shows and the video pauses, please repeat the sentence you have just heard. Keep practising until you can repeat perfectly!</p><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/brvfreukg7cnqndr1ifg\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D44L3R2.mp4 - 00:10\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span><br></p></div>",
